author: @anmolchaudhary3893
text: I think you have underfitted the model by doing only one epoch. I'm thinking about running a few epochs on a certain size of data (say 5 million pairs) before moving on to new data. It won't result in underfitting and if it running too many epochs results in overfitting then throwing more data will bring the high variance down.
